  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Inspect and verify the quantity of received goods as per Purchase/Delivery Orders, Invoices, or other relevant documentation.</li>\n  <li>Promptly report any damage or missing items to a superior during inspection.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that regulatory documents (e.g., from SFA, Customs) for imported goods are available upon receipt.</li>\n  <li>Store received goods in designated areas according to their temperature requirements to maintain cold chain control when necessary.</li>\n  <li>Accurately update inventory records in the Warehouse Management System and manual documentation.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a clean and safe working environment through regular housekeeping.</li>\n  <li>Assist with stock-taking and inventory counts.</li>\n  <li>Perform any other duties as assigned by a superior.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 3 years of experience as a Logistic Assistant/Storekeeper; HACCP/ISO/MUIS certification is preferred.</li>\n  <li>GCE “N” Level or higher, with basic computer skills.</li>\n  <li>Capable of handling heavy parcels/packages and operating heavy equipment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981| EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
